prompts.frontCover: Full-frame comic book panel illustration for a birthday card cover. A dynamic and funny beach scene featuring illustrated versions of Lao Lao (person on left in photo) and Jordan (person on right in photo). Lao Lao, wearing a light blue sweatshirt and glasses, is hilariously depicted as a superhero, "BEACH QUEEN," striking a powerful and confident pose in the center. She's comically holding a giant seashell like a trophy, grinning triumphantly. Jordan, in his tan hoodie, stands slightly behind her, cheering her on with an adoring and amused expression, holding up a giant, colorful birthday cake with lit candles. The background is a vibrant, stylized beach with exaggerated, bright blue rolling waves, golden sand, and a few quirky, cartoon crabs wearing tiny party hats. The sky is a bold sunset orange with classic comic book dot patterns (Ben-Day dots). In the center of the design, integrated into the scene, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" written in a fun, handwritten cursive script with a bold black outline. The entire image has the aesthetic of a vintage comic book, with thick black outlines, saturated colors, and a sense of action and humor. Flat 2D artwork.
